; TI-83 Plus application script
reset-calc
run 6000000
key-press on 6000000
key-press clear
key-press 2nd
key-press +
key-press 7
key-press left
key-press enter
key-press 2
send-file %DEBUG_BINARY%.8xk
key-press clear
key-press apps
key-press apps
key-press apps
key-press apps
key-press apps
key-press down
key-press enter